{"tid":1119232,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"closer","createTime":"2019-04-21T18:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T20:18:15.000Z","uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f97d102ed088c87a642ab189b9634254063cb38d","tid":1119232,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:55:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PMAB3r6EjcM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPMAB3r6EjcM&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6ouQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=0fe7c963\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PMAB3r6EjcM</a>"},{"pid":"ab91210ab6a768737d5e23d6e1697a6ebc57e491","tid":1119232,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:56:05.000Z","msg":"有時會懷疑 啊究竟點解會變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後知道問題根源係個自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定係自己 唔有其他<img src=\"https://beta-static.photobucket.com/images/ah233/sorsawsor/3/35234e1b-622a-4b20-964f-c69579770dcc-original.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeta-static.photobucket.com%2Fimages%2Fah233%2Fsorsawsor%2F3%2F35234e1b-622a-4b20-964f-c69579770dcc-original.gif&h=dd661daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果將所有嘢推返好前聽到會好難受事關我唔想聽同知<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知唔關我事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如今經已無咗個感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一旦認清就退卻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55cfc864ad7cdf957e9a518c92be38069a5f1e79","tid":1119232,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:00:00.000Z","msg":"這一生也在進取<br />\n這分鐘卻掛念誰"},{"pid":"6ee47acf8ed5e1a1afa8483c3909e8d9c1a05232","tid":1119232,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:06:24.000Z","msg":"瞓啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f1e35d50d0bea08a0c4ea94c5ee93141826a9a","tid":1119232,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:07:15.000Z","msg":"又覺得每個人都必須渡過一段相對漫長嘅一個時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擰返個頭轉去望會發現好多重要嘅累積都係咁完成<br />\n可能無門庭若市嘅熱鬧同觥籌交錯嘅喧嘩<br />\n係要mi埋個頭走沉落嚟面對自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係話浮起嚟唔好但有時自我嘅完善同能力嘅錘鍊只能夠係咁達成咁樣？等再返嚟時我諗我就可以創造到真正嘅嘞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係有好過無 不過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9975bf6104b13fd10e0a74e289c7b1b163656df1","tid":1119232,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55cfc864ad7cdf957e9a518c92be38069a5f1e79","tid":1119232,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:00:00.000Z","msg":"這一生也在進取<br />\n這分鐘卻掛念誰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:07:56.000Z","msg":"老餅"},{"pid":"43d757058526130ee8d0578607867edd2f631da1","tid":1119232,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ee47acf8ed5e1a1afa8483c3909e8d9c1a05232","tid":1119232,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:06:24.000Z","msg":"瞓啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:08:11.000Z","msg":"沉澱霞！"},{"pid":"ebc9e26fffd69a5ab7058f0c3e8437579b516804","tid":1119232,"uid":147916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43d757058526130ee8d0578607867edd2f631da1","tid":1119232,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ee47acf8ed5e1a1afa8483c39